item.description:
Workshops With Purpose-Humanitarian Photography-Travel Photography-Travel With Kids-Bolivia

In 2013, a group of world changing photographers embarked on a life changing adventure to Kijabe, Kenya ( blog post here). The photographers were the first group to take part in our co-led " Workshops With Purpose," a workshop designed to educate and equip them in the art of non-profit storytelling.
